---
title: Moroccan Sausage Stew with Fruity Couscous
description: Moroccan food has been heavily influenced by Berber, Moorish and Arab cuisine over the centuries and is alive with interesting flavours, textures and fragrances. This stew will take you on a taste trip to Morocco with a warmly spiced sauce and herby, nutty couscous, topped with crunchy almonds.
